---
// ES Yaşam - Selam Sayfası
---

<html lang="tr">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>Selam - ES Yaşam</title>
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
		<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
		<style>
			:root {
				--brand-gold: #d4af37;
				--brand-gold-dark: #c5a028;
				--brand-olive: #556b2f;
				--brand-olive-light: #8fbc8f;
				--bg-cream: #FAF8F5;
				--bg-cream-dark: #F5F2EB;
				--text-dark: #2c2520;
				--text-muted: #6e645e;
			}

			* {
				box-sizing: border-box;
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
			}

			body {
				font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
				background: radial-gradient(circle at top, var(--bg-cream) 0%, var(--bg-cream-dark) 100%);
				color: var(--text-dark);
				min-height: 100vh;
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: center;
				overflow-x: hidden;
				position: relative;
			}

			.container {
				max-width: 600px;
				width: 90%;
				text-align: center;
				padding: 3rem 2rem;
				border-radius: 24px;
				background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
				backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
				-webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
				border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.15);
				box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(44, 37, 32, 0.05);
				animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out;
			}

			.logo-wrapper {
				position: relative;
				display: inline-block;
				margin-bottom: 2rem;
			}

			.logo-img {
				width: 120px;
				height: 120px;
				border-radius: 50%;
				object-fit: cover;
				border: 3px solid var(--brand-gold);
				box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2);
			}

			h1 {
				font-size: 2.2rem;
				font-weight: 600;
				color: var(--text-dark);
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
			}

			h1 span {
				color: var(--brand-gold-dark);
			}

			.welcome-msg {
				font-size: 1.2rem;
				font-weight: 500;
				color: var(--brand-olive);
				margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
			}

			p.desc {
				font-size: 1rem;
				line-height: 1.6;
				color: var(--text-muted);
				margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
			}

			.btn {
				display: inline-block;
				width: 100%;
				padding: 1rem 2rem;
				background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-gold) 0%, var(--brand-gold-dark) 100%);
				color: white;
				text-decoration: none;
				border-radius: 12px;
				font-weight: 600;
				font-size: 1rem;
				box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3);
				transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
				border: none;
				cursor: pointer;
			}

			.btn:hover {
				transform: translateY(-3px);
				box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.4);
			}

			.footer {
				margin-top: 3rem;
				font-size: 0.85rem;
				color: var(--text-muted);
				opacity: 0.8;
			}

			@keyframes fadeIn {
				from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
				to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="container">
			<div class="logo-wrapper">
				<img src="/images/logo.jpg" alt="ES Yaşam Logo" class="logo-img" />
			</div>

			<h1>ES Yaşam'dan <span>Selamlar!</span></h1>
			<p class="welcome-msg">"Daha güzel bir yaşam için buradayız."</p>
			
			<p class="desc">
				Bu sayfa, GitHub ve Cloudflare Pages entegrasyonumuzun sorunsuz çalıştığını test etmek amacıyla oluşturulmuş geçici bir selamlaşma sayfasıdır..
			</p>

			<a href="/" class="btn">
				Ana Sayfaya Dön
			</a>
		</div>

		<div class="footer">
			© 2026 ES Yaşam & Uçbeyi Gıda. Tüm hakları saklıdır.
		</div>
	</body>
</html>





